## Purpose

This prompt compares strong-fit and weak-fit GTM Engineering job examples and creates a reusable classification rubric.

## Input

- BoB jobs
- WoW jobs

## Output

- GTME market-fit rubric
- Bucket definitions
- Positive and negative signals
- Scoring rules

